Chronicles 6:31	And these are they whom David set over the service of song in the house of Jehovah, after that the ark had rest.
Chronicles 6:32	And they ministered with song before the tabernacle of the tent of meeting, until Solomon had built the house of Jehovah in Jerusalem: and they waited on their office according to their order.
Chronicles 6:33	And these are they that waited, and their sons. Of the sons of the Kohathites: Heman the singer, the son of Joel, the son of Samuel,
